=head1 DESCRIPTION

Determines whether CloudFront includes the C<X-Content-Type-Options>
HTTP response header with its value set to C<nosniff>.

For more information about the C<X-Content-Type-Options> HTTP response
header, see X-Content-Type-Options
(https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/X-Content-Type-Options)
in the MDN Web Docs.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 B<REQUIRED> Override => Bool

A Boolean that determines whether CloudFront overrides the
C<X-Content-Type-Options> HTTP response header received from the origin
with the one specified in this response headers policy.



